APP_STATUS.md
IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md
CURRENT_STATUS.md
RESTART_*.md
SETUP_INSTRUCTIONS.md
SETUP_VERIFICATION.md
ANIMATION_VERIFICATION.md
LOCAL_TESTING_GUIDE.md
RATE_LIMIT_FIX.md

# Kiro specs and configuration
.kiro/

